**Root Mean Squared Error (RMSE):**
```
RMSE = ‚àö[(1/n) √ó Œ£(Actual - Forecast)¬≤]

Measures average forecast error in same units as target
Lower is better
```

**R¬≤ Score (Coefficient of Determination):**
```
R¬≤ = 1 - (SS_res / SS_tot)

Range: 0 to 1
- 1.0 = Perfect prediction
- 0.9+ = Excellent
- 0.7-0.9 = Good
- < 0.7 = Needs improvement
